<ptxt>
<emph etype = "bold">
P0133: O2 Sensor Circuit Slow Response (Sensor 1)
</emph>
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
Cycle duration from rich to lean and lean to rich of HO2S-1 is longer than specified time.
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
(Type A: 3 D/C detection logic)
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
(Type B: 2 D/C detection logic)
</ptxt>
</entry>
